{"tid":408732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[心涼] 麥紫莉左膝受傷痛哭送院治療","createTime":"2017-09-21T12:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T05:53:23.000Z","uid":92713,"like":1411,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed95f2283220d05ac93461ee180afd7afc076d73","tid":408732,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"正喺日本參與ViuTV製作《G-1格鬥會II》嘅麥紫莉(Chili)，經過一輪MMA訓練後今日正式上擂台，跟對手余智嘉(Chika)進行正式比賽。比賽過程完全係強弱懸殊，全程捱打嘅Chili更喺第二回合被對手Chika摔落地以Arm Bar鎖實，最後舉手示意投降。<br />\n<br />\n但Chili未能起身，仲喊住口大叫：「我起唔到身，好痛，膝頭好痛！」，然後教練就攞出冰袋替Chili敷住左膝，其間佢一直喊表現痛楚，由於受傷兼已經示意投降，評判就宣佈賽事結束。而Chili嘅教練就繼續為佢敷冰，攝製隊然後將Chili移至後台繼續治理。<br />\n<br />\n講番比賽，本身為健身教練，學過MMA同泰拳嘅Chika，喺首回合就已經主動進攻，將Chili摔落地再鎖實，不過Chili就奮力堅持到首回合結束。第二回合甫開始，Chika再度搶攻，不足廿秒已經將Chili打落地兼用Arm bar鎖實，本來Chili仍然想堅持落去，但無奈對手實力太強，令佢動彈不得，唯有拍地投降，但左腳膝蓋已經受傷。<br />\n<br />\n而ViuTV方面其後亦對Chili受傷作出回應： 「麥紫莉（Chili）於今日拍攝《G-1格鬥會 II》比賽期間受傷，ViuTV 為安全起見，已立即送她到就近醫院接受檢查。有進一步消息，ViuTV會稍後公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/204922_4e33ec337e6c40f05196c2504842bc99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F204922_4e33ec337e6c40f05196c2504842bc99.jpg&h=586589a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/204922_3893c1e7c78ee5b92ef0b0a2725a567c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F204922_3893c1e7c78ee5b92ef0b0a2725a567c.jpg&h=f8df7b59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/204923_3893c1e7c78ee5b92ef0b0a2725a567c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F204923_3893c1e7c78ee5b92ef0b0a2725a567c.jpg&h=10c8ebf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/204923_ba38a4948078ed5cc18b81719ff25fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F204923_ba38a4948078ed5cc18b81719ff25fef.jpg&h=bdfe458c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講大話係有報應㗎 大話精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打得好 唔使錫住條臭雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人哋好慘㗎 積吓口德分啦"},{"pid":"61e5c8c237ab0e1934efaddd5494bf2ad1ab405c","tid":408732,"uid":82398,"like":232,"dislike":5,"score":227,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"樓主正on9 幫條臭雞宣傳"},{"pid":"0d41e5d31f56699df817288cbda00772eccc8b16","tid":408732,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"唔記得擺返低個蘋果link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170921&amp;guid=57236957&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170921%26guid%3D57236957%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=mFNsu6F1qPnfRaHwWYJvpDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=61a88363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170921%26guid%3D57236957%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=6b09b655\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170921&amp;guid=57236957&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"c0c263516249d874c147cd164f5b76bbae7e6ef7","tid":408732,"uid":92713,"like":41,"dislike":4,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主正on9 幫條臭雞宣傳</blockquote><br />\n佢都就瘸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 